  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>An extensive breakfast buffet is served in the dining room or on the terrace each morning with a selection of pastries, cakes, bread, fruit, yoghurt, and hot options like scrambled eggs. There's also freshly brewed coffee and a variety of teas and juices to choose from. </p>
<p><strong>The Capri Restaurant </strong>has an à la carte menu for lunch and dinner (payable and bookable locally). The dinner menu changes daily and the cuisine combines regional traditions with Mediterranean favourites. It has beautiful panoramic views overlooking the lake. Open for breakfast between 7.30am - 10.30am, snack bar 12pm - 5.30pm and dinner between 7pm - 8.30pm. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
