  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Green Rooms</strong> sleep two people, are decorated in a modern style and have a balcony with lake views.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Garden View Rooms </strong>can sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a balcony with garden views. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Lake View Rooms </strong>can sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a balcony and lake views.</p>
<p>Please request twin or double beds at the time of booking.</p>
